          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Spread your <strong>tomato base</strong> equally over the <strong>toasted ciabatta[s]</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>torn mozzarella</strong>, <strong>sliced pepperoni </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>– this is your <strong>pepperoni pizza-style open sandwich[es]</strong></p>",
